Concepts

This case-insensitive code system http://ltsi.univ-rennes.fr/CodeSystem/snomedct defines codes in a Is-A hierarchy, but no codes are represented here

name: SNOMEDCT
title: SNOMED CT (all versions)
publisher: DOMASIA team of the Signal and Image Processing Laboratory (LTSI) and KEREVAL
